Author: Pink_salts
Text: Is it rumbling? If it’s rumbling and making odd noises it’s usually followed by diarrhea since your body is not used to such an influx of food so it passes the majority of it without properly breaking it down. You may be stranded on the toilet. Don’t trust your farts. Shart/fart into the toilet.

Author: deudeo
Text: This has happened to me before. I'm pretty sure it's your stomach shrinking and then getting way more food than it's prepared to handle.
